<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about classmethod)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/classmethod.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 Jul 2017 09:09:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Python构造对象编号自动加一</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/pythongou-zao-dui-xiang-bian-hao-zi-dong-jia-yi/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
这是一个Python中类方法的使用案例。&lt;/blockquote&gt;
